m the house of slavery."]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":["I sent Moses before you,"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["as well as Aaron and Miriam."]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":[{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"5"},"My people, remember what Balak king of Moab counseled"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["and what Balaam son of Beor answered."]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":["Remember your journey from Shittim",{"type":"note","marker":"f","content":[{"type":"char","marker":"fr","content":["6:5"]},{"type":"char","marker":"ft","content":["Or ",{"type":"char","marker":"fq","content":["Acacia Grove"]}]}],"caller":"+"},"to Gilgal,"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["so that you may acknowledge the righteousness of the LORD.’”"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":[{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"6"},"With what shall I come before the LORD"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["when I bow before the God on high?"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":["Should I come to Him with burnt offerings,"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["with year-old calves?"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":[{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"7"},"Would the LORD be pleased with thousands of rams,"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["with ten thousand rivers of oil?"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":["Shall I present my firstborn for my transgression,"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["the fruit of my body for the sin of my soul?"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":[{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"8"},"He has shown you, O man, what is good."]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["And what does the LORD require of you"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q1","content":["but to act justly, to love mercy,"]},{"type":"para","marker":"q2","content":["and to walk humbly with your God?"]},{"type":"para","marker":"s1","content":["The Punishment of Israel"]},{"type":"para",